snippet.title: Hitman Party - Announcement Trailer | PC
snippet.description:
Get ready to join the ultimate hitman party - a fast-paced and hilarious local multiplayer game for up to 6 players. Can you blend in with the crowd, outsmart your friends, and be the first to hunt down the target? Experience the thrill of multiple game modes with your friends!

Wishlist on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1815290/Hitman_Party/

Visit our website: https://www.hitmanparty.com
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/NewheadStudio

Song:
Hall of the Mountain King
Link: https://filmmusic.io/song/6167-bossa-of-margie-instrumental
License: https://filmmusic.io/standard-license
